Package: restbatch
Type: Package
Title: A Simple 'RESTful' Web Service to Schedule R Batch Jobs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Zhengjia", "Wang", email = "dipterix.wang@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Starts web services accepting 'http' requests, automatically
    receive, schedule and scale the tasks via the package 'batchtools' as
    the backend. Provides integration to monitor the submitted tasks in 
    'RStudio' or 'Shiny' apps.
URL: https://github.com/dipterix/restbatch
BugReports: https://github.com/dipterix/restbatch/issues
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-US
LazyData: true
